{"tid":1609279,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online 職業分類","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T22:17:19.000Z","uid":34665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b91d5b106b2cb17a3884b0740c9cdf527efeb17e","tid":1609279,"uid":34665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"今日明顯突出左各分散區打副本係有效嘅，而大家打左咁耐機，除左一部分天賦異稟嘅人有明顯職業導向（eg:魔法師、哨兵）之外<br />\n大部分人對自己嘅職業唔多明確<br />\n故此，我希望大家下次online之前，諗定會做咩職業<br />\n職業大致劃分如下<br />\n1. 魔法師（火水土光......等等有待開發）<br />\n2. 哨兵<br />\n3. 弓手（即有強大投擲能力之人）<br />\n4. 遊騎兵（主要打快閃擾敵）<br />\n5. 工兵（主力從事工地建築及物資提供）<br />\n6. 運輸兵（係轉場時幫助物資快速轉移）<br />\n7. 通訊兵（係打副本提供準確嘅敵方消息）<br />\n8. 最重要嘅前線肉搏<br />\n以上為粗略劃分，期待開創更多職業<br />\n亦可以一人身兼數職<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝武運昌隆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2d0be6931d567215d76921009762ff8f2f88733c","tid":1609279,"uid":34665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:12:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd98d8ae6a9b4561a7d722b49f2eb038682257ee","tid":1609279,"uid":34665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:12:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5909062fb8f01c1728d40e71a7cc4c0a987444b3","tid":1609279,"uid":324246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"仲有馴獸師，負責控制獅鳥"},{"pid":"134a86ff6183aae1c37d8d7ee0d17594c5e3d48c","tid":1609279,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c6c736e6fcab59f720fea48d30a55d1e42f7aaa","tid":1609279,"uid":396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T22:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}